                    <h1>Join us!</h1>
</br>
<p>There are several ways for you to get involved with Teach4Morocco:</p>
</br>
<p><b>Volunteer your Skills -</b> We are always looking for volunteers who can help us out
with specific tasks. Our next field project will be in summer 2013 and we are looking
for volunteers for construction, painting, coordinating activities, etc.</p>
</br>
<p><b>Donate -</b> We accept two types of donations:
1. We are more than happy to accept fiscal donations to Teach4Morocco's Bank
account:</br></br>

Al Barid Bank</br>
Agence: MEKNES PPAL 0300</br>
Numero de compte: 5007443</br>
Intitul&eacute;: Teach For Morocco</br>
</br>
For further details please contact: Laziri@gmail.com</br></p>
</br>
<p>2. We are also accepting donations of tools or materials to be used for constructing
schools.</p>
</br>
<p><b>Partner with us -</b> We would like to work with like-minded NGOs globally. We have
teamed up with a French student-run NGO, Interface IEP, to reconstruct a school in
summer 2012. Please see our -What we do- section for more.</p>
</br>
<p><b>Share your ideas and suggestions -</b> We welcome your ideas and suggestions. Please feel free to
email our team to share you ideas, expertise and skills.</p>
</br>
<p><b>Spread the Word -</b> please help make Teach4Morocco known among your friends
and family by telling them about it.</p>
                    
